<div class="slide_question">
<h2>On average, which treatment costs the most?</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q5" name="q5" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>Microdermabrasion</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>A chemical peel</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="c" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">c</div>
<p>Intense pulsed light treatment</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">15</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>On average, which treatment costs the most?</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>A chemical peel costs about $644, according to the American Society of Plastic Surgery. A microdermabrasion session costs about $136. Intense pulsed light (IPL) treatment, a light therapy that can improve skin color and texture, averages more than $406 per procedure. &lt;2019 average pricing&gt;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
