<div class="slide_question">
<h2>You can get a chemical peel on:</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q9" name="q9" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>Just your face</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>Your face and neck</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="c" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">c</div>
<p>Your face, neck, chest, and hands</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">15</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>You can get a chemical peel on:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Chemical peeling isn't just for your face. It can be used on just about any sun-damaged skin. A peel removes skin cells and reduces age spots, irregular coloring, rough skin, and freckles. It's also good for fine lines, especially near the eyes and mouth. Chemicals wouldn't be used on your eyes or lips.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="slide_controls">
<ul>
<li class="next">
<hr/>
<a class="rmq_next" href="#" title="Continue">
