<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">15</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>Deep chemical peels may be more likely to cause skin problems if you have:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
