<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Among various types of laser therapy, one called non-ablative laser rejuvenation -- the kind that leaves the top layer of skin intact and targets the skin underneath -- works well for early signs of aging.</p>
</div>
